♪It's a vow of day and night♪

14
00:01:32,890 --> 00:01:37,200
[Blooming]

15
00:01:37,360 --> 00:01:39,920
[Episode 18]

16
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:42,680
Although the love between Hu Meng
and Zhu Yan is lamentable,

17
00:01:43,080 --> 00:01:45,000
at least Zhu Yan is a faithful man.

18
00:01:45,280 --> 00:01:47,520
Hu Meng's love for him is not wasted.

19
00:01:48,040 --> 00:01:48,880
Cui Chen, on the contrary,

20
00:01:49,360 --> 00:01:50,200
is full of righteousness and morality,

21
00:01:50,600 --> 00:01:51,760
yet he treats love so casually.

22
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:53,800
You don't deserve this.

23
00:01:56,400 --> 00:01:58,080
I don't care. Why are you so angry?

24
00:01:59,880 --> 00:02:00,440
I've made up my mind.

25
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:01,680
From now on,

26
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:04,480
I won't be upset about him anymore.

27
00:02:05,160 --> 00:02:07,680
Tantan, it's good that you think so.

28
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:10,240
As long as you're happy, I'm happy.

29
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:16,200
Tantan, you...

30
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:17,200
Don't get me wrong.

31
00:02:17,720 --> 00:02:18,400
I didn't.

32
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:18,680
I didn't.

33
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:19,720
I...

34
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:22,480
I just think I'm so lucky

35
00:02:22,920 --> 00:02:24,520
to have met a man as kind as you.

36
00:02:25,920 --> 00:02:26,520
That's not true.

37
00:02:27,680 --> 00:02:28,800
In fact, I have a selfish motive.

38
00:02:29,720 --> 00:02:30,200
I did it all for you.

39
00:02:30,200 --> 00:02:30,400
I did it all for you.

40
00:02:32,760 --> 00:02:34,920
I'm the future Light of Qingyuan.

41
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:37,000
That's not selfish to help me.

42
00:02:39,160 --> 00:02:41,040
We can almost think

43
00:02:41,040 --> 00:02:41,720
you

44
00:02:42,320 --> 00:02:44,640
are enterprising in cultivation.

45
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:50,760
Tantan,

46
00:02:52,120 --> 00:02:53,520
I'm different from Cui Chen.

47
00:02:54,200 --> 00:02:55,520
All he thinks about
is helping the world.

48
00:02:56,160 --> 00:02:57,680
But I only want to be with you,

49
00:02:58,720 --> 00:02:59,600
like now,

50
00:03:00,320 --> 00:03:01,480
having fun with you, laughing with you.

51
00:03:02,160 --> 00:03:02,760
Do you like it?

52
00:03:04,160 --> 00:03:04,560
Yeah.

53
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:05,840
Thanks, Qiu.

54
00:03:07,840 --> 00:03:08,320
Tantan,

55
00:03:09,320 --> 00:03:10,520
I mean,

56
00:03:11,040 --> 00:03:12,720
I don't want us to be just friends.

57
00:03:13,480 --> 00:03:14,680
I want us to take it to the next level.

58
00:03:14,760 --> 00:03:15,000
You...

59
00:03:16,040 --> 00:03:16,720
Do you understand?

60
00:03:17,920 --> 00:03:19,840
The next level?

61
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:23,320
OK.

62
00:03:24,080 --> 00:03:25,920
Great idea. I agree.

63
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:26,840
Really?

64
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:28,400
I'll tell you what, I've decided

65
00:03:28,880 --> 00:03:30,040
that from tomorrow on,

66
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:32,560
I'll teach you mental methods
and mnemonic rhyme.

67
00:03:35,160 --> 00:03:36,000
What do you mean?

68
00:03:36,880 --> 00:03:37,760
Are you saying...

69
00:03:38,440 --> 00:03:38,920
Didn't you suggest

70
00:03:38,920 --> 00:03:40,240
we take our relationship
to the next level?

71
00:03:41,040 --> 00:03:41,640
Look,

72
00:03:41,880 --> 00:03:43,440
the weather, air,
and moon are all perfect today.

73
00:03:44,040 --> 00:03:44,880
Let me take you as my disciple.

74
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:48,800
You...

75
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:50,520
To take our relationship
to the next level,

76
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:51,720
do you mean to take me as your disciple?

77
00:03:52,200 --> 00:03:52,760
Yes.

78
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:54,760
If I take you as my disciple,

79
00:03:55,080 --> 00:03:56,040
you won't just

80
00:03:56,040 --> 00:03:57,520
be there for me as a friend.

81
00:03:57,720 --> 00:03:59,080
You will

82
00:03:59,240 --> 00:04:00,760
be there for me

83
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:01,880
as my glorious first disciple.

84
00:04:04,920 --> 00:04:06,280
Tantan, actually...

85
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:08,760
Let's formalize
our master-disciple relationship.

86
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:10,760
But

87
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:12,520
I've seen others taking disciples.

88
00:04:13,200 --> 00:04:16,270
Disciples are supposed to burn incense,
bathe, and kowtow.

89
00:04:17,390 --> 00:04:18,680
Why don't you go and get ready?

90
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:20,600
Forget it.

91
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:22,200
Come on.

92
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:22,360
No.

93
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:23,320
Get up.

94
00:04:23,320 --> 00:04:23,760
No.

95
00:04:24,440 --> 00:04:26,440
Qiu, you know what,

96
00:04:26,960 --> 00:04:28,720
I'm so grateful to you.

97
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:32,040
You've helped me find my goal in life.

98
00:04:32,200 --> 00:04:35,680
From now on,
I won't be concerned with love.

99
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:37,680
I'll focus on my career.

100
00:04:41,120 --> 00:04:41,480
Tantan,

101
00:04:42,280 --> 00:04:43,600
I don't think we should rush

102
00:04:43,840 --> 00:04:45,120
into taking our relationship

103
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:46,120
to the next level.

104
00:04:46,280 --> 00:04:46,840
No rush.

105
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:48,360
I tell you what,

106
00:04:49,320 --> 00:04:50,640
we're in a rush to find the lotus seeds.

107
00:04:50,840 --> 00:04:53,000
Let's wait until I pay homage
to my grand master,

108
00:04:53,280 --> 00:04:54,400
then we'll go over the details...

109
00:04:54,880 --> 00:04:55,680
Don't bother.

110
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:57,320
Your grand master listens to me.
Come on.

111
00:04:58,320 --> 00:04:58,920
Hurry.

112
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:00,040
I don't think

113
00:05:00,840 --> 00:05:01,840
it's that urgent.

114
00:05:02,520 --> 00:05:02,960
Some other day.

115
00:05:03,200 --> 00:05:03,840
Next time.

116
00:05:03,880 --> 00:05:04,520
Qiu, don't leave.

117
00:05:04,520 --> 00:05:05,480
- Next time. I'm off.
- Don't go.

118
00:05:05,520 --> 00:05:06,600
You asked to be my disciple.

119
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:07,200
Come back.

120
00:05:07,200 --> 00:05:07,600
Next time.

121
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:09,760
He's so weird.

122
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:11,200
Didn't he ask to be my disciple?

123
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:25,360
Everyone in the town is sleeping.

124
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:26,840
Do you think we can get the new quilts

125
00:05:26,840 --> 00:05:27,840
from the silk shop now?

126
00:05:28,640 --> 00:05:29,240
I guess so.

127
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:31,400
The boss's wife told us yesterday

128
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:32,600
that they were going to

129
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:33,960
deliver new clothes to Mr. Wang

130
00:05:33,960 --> 00:05:35,000
in the next town over at noon today.

131
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:37,680
They should be awake by now.

132
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:40,240
How was your conversation
with Qiu Yuebai yesterday?

133
00:05:41,960 --> 00:05:42,520
Pretty good.

134
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:45,000
I've decided to take him as my disciple.

135
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:48,960
Disciple?

136
00:05:48,960 --> 00:05:51,720
[Zhou's Silk Shop]

137
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:52,160
Tantan.

138
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:59,160
They're still sleeping at this hour.

139
00:05:59,280 --> 00:06:00,840
Aren't they going to
deliver clothes to Mr. Wang?

140
00:06:06,080 --> 00:06:06,520
Madam.

141
00:06:07,640 --> 00:06:08,120
Madam.

142
00:06:08,840 --> 00:06:10,600
Go and pick for yourself.

143
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:13,320
I'm sleepy.

144
00:06:14,160 --> 00:06:14,560
Sir.

145
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:16,240
Sir. Wake up. Sir.

146
00:06:16,520 --> 00:06:17,080
Leave me alone.

147
00:06:19,920 --> 00:06:20,800
They are fast asleep.

148
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:22,120
Aren't they afraid of being stolen?

149
00:06:22,240 --> 00:06:23,360
We'd better not wake them up.

150
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,360
Let's pick quilts ourselves

151
00:06:24,560 --> 00:06:25,360
and leave them the money.

152
00:06:25,880 --> 00:06:26,240
OK.

153
00:06:31,520 --> 00:06:33,280
Don't take this one.
I'll pick one for you.

154
00:06:36,520 --> 00:06:37,000
This one.

155
00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:39,560
This one is soft, silky, light,
and dense.

156
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:40,680
It should be cozier.

157
00:06:41,640 --> 00:06:42,400
You know what,

158
00:06:42,760 --> 00:06:44,760
I used to play in the mountain
behind the Qingyuan Sect.

159
00:06:44,760 --> 00:06:46,800
When I was tired,
I'd just find a tree to sleep in.

160
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:48,240
I was a wild girl.

161
00:06:48,480 --> 00:06:50,400
How can I recognize a good quilt?

162
00:06:51,160 --> 00:06:53,360
But I'll listen to you today.

163
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:55,440
I'm going to enjoy the good quilt.

164
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:56,040
Go.

165
00:06:58,160 --> 00:06:58,800
We each take our own.

166
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:00,040
OK

167
00:07:00,800 --> 00:07:01,120
Go.

168
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:06,440
Why did I

169
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:07,560
fall asleep last night?

170
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:10,680
If I'd held on just a little longer,

171
00:07:10,760 --> 00:07:13,160
this wouldn't have ended up like this.

172
00:07:14,520 --> 00:07:15,640
That's true, Uncle.

173
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:16,760
Cui Chen had worked so hard

174
00:07:16,960 --> 00:07:18,440
to make the arrangement.

175
00:07:18,760 --> 00:07:19,760
And what happened?

176
00:07:20,080 --> 00:07:21,720
Qiu Yuebai took advantage of it.

177
00:07:22,320 --> 00:07:23,640
I'm so pissed.

178
00:07:24,200 --> 00:07:24,560
Huai Meng.

179
00:07:27,280 --> 00:07:27,960
What are you talking about?

180
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:32,560
Did Cui Chen
decorate the courtyard last night?

181
00:07:32,840 --> 00:07:33,800
You're right.

182
00:07:34,560 --> 00:07:36,520
He prepared the candlesticks, flowers,

183
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:38,280
and two bottles of wine.

184
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:39,520
Darn it.

185
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:40,720
In the end...

186
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:43,600
It was so cold last night.

187
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:44,800
Exactly.

188
00:07:44,960 --> 00:07:45,720
Cui Chen

189
00:07:46,080 --> 00:07:48,080
worked his butt off.

190
00:07:48,480 --> 00:07:50,040
He even caught a cold
and couldn't get out of bed.

191
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:50,560
Uncle.

192
00:07:50,640 --> 00:07:51,400
But no one's been to see him.

193
00:07:51,400 --> 00:07:51,880
Uncle.

194
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:53,760
What?

195
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:55,440
Shouldn't we defend Cui Chen...

196
00:07:56,920 --> 00:07:57,240
Morning.

197
00:07:57,840 --> 00:07:59,120
What are you doing here at this moment?

198
00:08:03,520 --> 00:08:06,360
Didn't you say he caught a cold
and couldn't get out of bed?

199
00:08:07,760 --> 00:08:08,800
Cold.

200
00:08:10,640 --> 00:08:11,400
Poor kid.

201
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:15,640
Cui Chen.

202
00:08:15,960 --> 00:08:16,320
Cui Chen.

203
00:08:16,640 --> 00:08:17,080
Look.

204
00:08:18,400 --> 00:08:18,880
What's wrong?

205
00:08:18,960 --> 00:08:20,080
Why did you come at such a bad time?

206
00:08:20,200 --> 00:08:21,000
What happened?

207
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:21,320
Gosh.

208
00:08:21,320 --> 00:08:22,760
Cui Chen, you made me speechless.

209
00:08:32,800 --> 00:08:35,480
Could the new quilt
really attract the spirit?

210
00:08:36,160 --> 00:08:38,160
I don't know. Give it a try.

211
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:51,560
Cui Chen.

212
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:52,600
Cui Chen.

213
00:08:53,400 --> 00:08:53,840
Cui Chen.

214
00:08:54,120 --> 00:08:54,520
Tantan.

215
00:08:54,640 --> 00:08:56,000
Don't leave me, Cui Chen.

216
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:56,680
Tantan.

217
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:58,680
Don't leave me.

218
00:09:05,720 --> 00:09:06,760
What's that smell?

219
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:08,080
Herbal ointment.

220
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:11,280
The spirit made you sleep just now.

221
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:12,480
It was a white mist.

222
00:09:13,120 --> 00:09:13,880
It escaped through the door.

223
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:15,680
How dare it stab me in the back?!

224
00:09:16,040 --> 00:09:16,320
Go!

225
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:17,440
Hurry.

226
00:09:20,200 --> 00:09:22,400
Cui Chen is running
after the white mist.

227
00:09:23,400 --> 00:09:23,680
Go.

228
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:02,440
Tantan.

229
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:07,040
Cover it with your toad coat.

230
00:11:12,040 --> 00:11:12,320
This is...

231
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:13,680
Quilt?

232
00:11:14,040 --> 00:11:16,000
Could a quilt become a spirit
these days?

233
00:11:16,400 --> 00:11:18,040
As far as I know, it's a succubae.

234
00:11:18,520 --> 00:11:19,720
Probably, it's a cotton spirit.

235
00:11:20,200 --> 00:11:21,400
Reaching a certain level,

236
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:22,640
it can weave itself into a quilt,

237
00:11:22,640 --> 00:11:24,080
so that the cotton gathers
and won't fall apart.

238
00:11:24,640 --> 00:11:27,520
You're bullying me!

239
00:11:28,080 --> 00:11:29,320
What kind of immortal is this?

240
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:30,360
Immortal?

241
00:11:31,400 --> 00:11:33,440
This little thing
is 300 years old at most.

242
00:11:33,760 --> 00:11:36,080
In terms of seniority, I'm her ancestor.

243
00:11:36,680 --> 00:11:40,040
You're bullying me!

244
00:11:40,520 --> 00:11:42,360
What's going on here?

245
00:11:42,640 --> 00:11:45,160
Has the cotton shrunk in water?

246
00:11:50,160 --> 00:11:51,760
Stop crying.

247
00:11:52,360 --> 00:11:53,040
Stop crying.

248
00:11:53,040 --> 00:11:55,800
I was trying to help you,

249
00:11:56,080 --> 00:11:58,080
but you treat me badly.

250
00:11:58,080 --> 00:12:00,280
You're so mean!

251
00:12:01,760 --> 00:12:04,160
Look, you've hurt me badly!

252
00:12:07,360 --> 00:12:09,240
Though children speak the truth,

253
00:12:09,480 --> 00:12:11,240
you should speak from your conscience.

254
00:12:11,520 --> 00:12:12,920
Look, the whole town can't wake

255
00:12:13,040 --> 00:12:14,760
from a long sleep because of you.

256
00:12:15,200 --> 00:12:16,680
You call this helping them?

257
00:12:16,680 --> 00:12:18,840
I'm trying to be nice.

258
00:12:19,000 --> 00:12:22,000
Why are you scolding me?

259
00:12:23,920 --> 00:12:24,640
You're injured.

260
00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:26,920
Let me apply medicine to your wound, OK?

261
00:12:29,800 --> 00:12:30,760
Come with me.

262
00:12:31,880 --> 00:12:32,600
Come on.

263
00:12:41,400 --> 00:12:41,840
Little girl,

264
00:12:42,560 --> 00:12:44,400
my name is Qiu Yuebai. What's your name?

265
00:12:44,520 --> 00:12:45,760
Bai Diezi.

266
00:12:46,600 --> 00:12:47,560
Bai Diezi.

267
00:12:47,960 --> 00:12:49,280
What did you mean when you said

268
00:12:49,720 --> 00:12:50,480
you were helping them?

269
00:12:50,960 --> 00:12:52,520
They said it themselves.

270
00:12:53,040 --> 00:12:55,080
They can't get out of their quilts
in the morning.

271
00:12:55,520 --> 00:12:58,160
When they get home at night,
they flake out in bed.

272
00:12:58,880 --> 00:13:02,480
They wish they could stay in bed
all day.

273
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:04,640
Some adults suffer from sleeplessness.

274
00:13:04,960 --> 00:13:06,880
They can't sleep
even though they want to.

275
00:13:07,440 --> 00:13:09,680
So I feel sorry for them.

276
00:13:09,920 --> 00:13:12,360
I let them have what they want
and sleep all the time.

277
00:13:16,960 --> 00:13:18,760
It seems that
we should really thank you.

278
00:13:21,120 --> 00:13:21,760
What's this?

279
00:13:22,240 --> 00:13:22,800
No.

280
00:13:23,680 --> 00:13:24,120
Don't touch it.

281
00:13:27,160 --> 00:13:29,600
Little girl, this is so beautiful.

282
00:13:29,800 --> 00:13:31,280
May I have a look at it?

283
00:13:31,280 --> 00:13:31,960
