Tantan, I want to eat
while having my hair combed.

572
00:26:11,680 --> 00:26:12,640
Clumsy.

573
00:26:13,680 --> 00:26:14,000
OK.

574
00:26:15,160 --> 00:26:16,400
You clever little thing.

575
00:26:17,000 --> 00:26:18,080
Why do you have so many ideas?

576
00:26:23,960 --> 00:26:24,800
Is it flying high?

577
00:26:24,800 --> 00:26:25,680
It's high.

578
00:26:26,320 --> 00:26:27,120
I want it to be higher.

579
00:26:27,120 --> 00:26:27,720
Higher?

580
00:26:27,960 --> 00:26:28,880
Bai Diezi, I'll give it to you.

581
00:26:29,080 --> 00:26:29,920
You mustn't lose it.

582
00:26:30,040 --> 00:26:30,880
Let me try.

583
00:26:30,880 --> 00:26:31,560
Ready?

584
00:26:33,720 --> 00:26:34,240
This.

585
00:26:35,000 --> 00:26:35,400
Here.

586
00:26:37,240 --> 00:26:38,040
- Cui Chen.
- What's this?

587
00:26:40,360 --> 00:26:40,800
Peaches.

588
00:26:47,120 --> 00:26:48,840
(Tantan doesn't like Yuebai.)

589
00:26:49,160 --> 00:26:50,080
(I must find a way to help him.)

590
00:26:50,080 --> 00:26:51,760
Let's clean these peaches.

591
00:26:52,200 --> 00:26:52,800
Tantan,

592
00:26:54,320 --> 00:26:56,720
don't you want my lotus seed?

593
00:27:00,120 --> 00:27:02,400
Bai Diezi, why are you talking

594
00:27:02,400 --> 00:27:03,680
about the lotus seed suddenly?

595
00:27:04,760 --> 00:27:05,560
Don't get us wrong.

596
00:27:06,080 --> 00:27:06,880
We do

597
00:27:06,920 --> 00:27:08,880
want this lotus seed.

598
00:27:09,520 --> 00:27:10,960
But we also like you

599
00:27:11,200 --> 00:27:12,080
and want to play with you.

600
00:27:12,160 --> 00:27:13,600
I know you are good to me.

601
00:27:13,760 --> 00:27:15,000
I like you too.

602
00:27:15,640 --> 00:27:17,000
Yuebai likes you too.

603
00:27:17,920 --> 00:27:20,440
If you agree to be with Yuebai,

604
00:27:20,720 --> 00:27:22,880
I'll give you the lotus seed as a gift.

605
00:27:27,000 --> 00:27:28,400
That way the three of us

606
00:27:28,440 --> 00:27:29,880
will be together all the time.

607
00:27:33,760 --> 00:27:35,800
Bai Diezi, listen to me.

608
00:27:35,920 --> 00:27:38,080
You're a little girl.
You don't know about relationships.

609
00:27:38,640 --> 00:27:40,800
You can't be with someone
just because you want to.

610
00:27:42,760 --> 00:27:44,720
Adults always make simple things

611
00:27:44,720 --> 00:27:45,800
complicated.

612
00:27:46,440 --> 00:27:50,160
We've had so much fun these days.

613
00:27:50,600 --> 00:27:53,040
I want Yuebai to be my father
and you to be my mother.

614
00:27:53,360 --> 00:27:54,040
That would be great!

615
00:27:55,720 --> 00:27:56,320
Bai Diezi,

616
00:27:57,440 --> 00:27:59,520
I can be your father too.

617
00:28:00,400 --> 00:28:01,040
Yes, you can.

618
00:28:02,200 --> 00:28:04,040
Look, good girl.

619
00:28:04,280 --> 00:28:05,000
I didn't care for you in vain.

620
00:28:05,160 --> 00:28:07,160
But you can only be my godfather.

621
00:28:12,480 --> 00:28:14,080
I didn't tell her to say that.

622
00:28:14,080 --> 00:28:15,520
Yeah. It has nothing to do with Yuebai.

623
00:28:15,680 --> 00:28:16,760
It's my own idea.

624
00:28:16,960 --> 00:28:18,440
Am I not as good to you
as Qiu Yuebai is?

625
00:28:18,440 --> 00:28:20,760
No bad guy is as good as my father.

626
00:28:21,000 --> 00:28:21,880
You just can't.

627
00:28:22,160 --> 00:28:22,960
Why can't I?

628
00:28:23,080 --> 00:28:23,960
Today I must let you...

629
00:28:23,960 --> 00:28:24,880
Enough.

630
00:28:25,200 --> 00:28:27,880
Why are you arguing with a kid?

631
00:28:28,200 --> 00:28:29,640
I think it's a good idea.

632
00:28:29,800 --> 00:28:31,840
An innocent child
is the best judge of human nature.

633
00:28:32,360 --> 00:28:34,000
She knows who's good to her.

634
00:28:34,280 --> 00:28:35,040
That's right.

635
00:28:35,040 --> 00:28:36,800
Isn't a godfather a father?

636
00:28:37,120 --> 00:28:39,040
Senior Mu Bai,
why are you so calculating?

637
00:28:39,360 --> 00:28:41,680
An innocent child is easy to be fooled.

638
00:28:42,120 --> 00:28:42,720
Mr. Qiu,

639
00:28:43,320 --> 00:28:46,120
you don't think that if you
use the lotus seed as a threat,

640
00:28:46,280 --> 00:28:47,680
Tantan will give in, do you?

641
00:28:47,800 --> 00:28:50,000
Mr. Qiu, how could you do that?

642
00:28:50,120 --> 00:28:52,240
Xueyi, cut it out.

643
00:28:52,400 --> 00:28:53,160
Why can't I say it?

644
00:28:53,160 --> 00:28:54,920
Don't talk bad about Yuebai!

645
00:28:55,080 --> 00:28:55,560
Don't!

646
00:28:55,560 --> 00:28:56,120
Enough.

647
00:28:56,360 --> 00:28:57,000
Stop arguing.

648
00:28:58,400 --> 00:28:58,920
Come here.

649
00:28:59,880 --> 00:29:02,120
Bai Diezi, listen to me carefully.

650
00:29:02,800 --> 00:29:04,240
I just think of Yuebai

651
00:29:04,280 --> 00:29:05,280
as a friend.

652
00:29:05,520 --> 00:29:06,520
It won't change.

653
00:29:07,000 --> 00:29:08,240
If you must

654
00:29:08,240 --> 00:29:09,960
ask me to be with him,

655
00:29:10,560 --> 00:29:12,320
I won't accept your lotus seed.

656
00:29:12,760 --> 00:29:13,360
Tantan.

657
00:29:13,560 --> 00:29:14,040
Tantan.

658
00:29:15,040 --> 00:29:15,600
Tantan.

659
00:29:17,600 --> 00:29:19,040
Tantan, don't go.

660
00:29:21,320 --> 00:29:23,160
What's wrong with Qiu Yuebai?

661
00:29:23,320 --> 00:29:25,000
How could he use a child?

662
00:29:25,760 --> 00:29:26,480
Exactly.

663
00:29:28,520 --> 00:29:30,400
Bro, I'm telling you,

664
00:29:30,720 --> 00:29:31,960
you're in trouble.

665
00:29:32,440 --> 00:29:34,080
If you don't get the lotus seed,

666
00:29:34,400 --> 00:29:34,680
then

667
00:29:34,840 --> 00:29:36,240
Tantan won't make up with you.

668
00:29:36,280 --> 00:29:38,280
But Bai Diezi was right about one thing.

669
00:29:38,840 --> 00:29:40,720
Adults always make things complicated.

670
00:29:41,280 --> 00:29:42,480
As long as Tantan likes Cui Chen,

671
00:29:42,720 --> 00:29:44,400
whether he gets the lotus seed or not,

672
00:29:44,800 --> 00:29:46,240
Tantan will make up with him.

673
00:29:46,680 --> 00:29:47,400
Is it really that simple?

674
00:29:47,640 --> 00:29:48,760
It won't be that simple.

675
00:29:49,680 --> 00:29:50,400
Believe me,

676
00:29:50,400 --> 00:29:51,920
Qiu Yuebai won't stop so easily.

677
00:29:52,720 --> 00:29:53,120
Gosh.

678
00:29:54,760 --> 00:29:55,360
Uncle,

679
00:29:55,880 --> 00:29:58,360
how many women have you dated
in your 5,000 years of life?

680
00:29:59,280 --> 00:30:00,160
Properly speaking,

681
00:30:00,360 --> 00:30:01,680
I've had about 50 true loves.

682
00:30:02,240 --> 00:30:03,200
Why are you asking me this?

683
00:30:03,640 --> 00:30:04,440
Gosh, Uncle,

684
00:30:04,480 --> 00:30:05,440
I know you too well.

685
00:30:06,240 --> 00:30:07,600
Bro, don't be afraid.

686
00:30:08,400 --> 00:30:10,680
You mustn't give up on Tantan.

687
00:30:11,080 --> 00:30:11,880
Don't let her go easily.

688
00:30:12,200 --> 00:30:13,120
Go straight to her

689
00:30:13,120 --> 00:30:14,080
and say what's on your mind.

690
00:30:14,480 --> 00:30:15,080
You know what,

691
00:30:15,720 --> 00:30:16,880
though she likes you now,

692
00:30:17,480 --> 00:30:18,640
she may dislike you

693
00:30:18,880 --> 00:30:20,040
and be disappointed in you at any time.

694
00:30:20,200 --> 00:30:22,040
Who hasn't been in a relationship?

695
00:30:22,720 --> 00:30:23,960
But I agree with you on this.

696
00:30:24,640 --> 00:30:26,360
The best defense is offense.

697
00:30:26,800 --> 00:30:28,680
Let's be patient, OK?

698
00:30:28,800 --> 00:30:30,000
A long delay means many hitches.

699
00:30:30,360 --> 00:30:31,600
He must act fast.

700
00:30:31,600 --> 00:30:33,520
Bro, you must listen to me and Hu Meng.

701
00:30:34,080 --> 00:30:35,120
You must listen to me.

702
00:30:35,560 --> 00:30:36,880
- Listen to us.
- Listen to me.

703
00:30:40,280 --> 00:30:40,960
Listen to us.

704
00:30:40,960 --> 00:30:41,960
I'm telling you, he must listen to us.

705
00:30:41,960 --> 00:30:43,520
Do you know
how many times I've been dumped?

706
00:30:43,520 --> 00:30:45,120
You deserve it.

707
00:32:03,040 --> 00:32:03,520
What's wrong?

708
00:32:04,960 --> 00:32:05,480
Something on your mind?

709
00:32:07,440 --> 00:32:08,080
I'm sorry.

710
00:32:08,440 --> 00:32:09,680
Did I wake you up?

711
00:32:09,960 --> 00:32:10,520
No.

712
00:32:10,800 --> 00:32:12,160
I woke up when I turned over.

713
00:32:26,960 --> 00:32:28,160
You're worrying about something.

714
00:32:29,200 --> 00:32:30,160
Why don't you tell me?

715
00:32:30,200 --> 00:32:30,960
I may give you some advice.

716
00:32:34,520 --> 00:32:36,600
Actually, it wasn't me.

717
00:32:37,280 --> 00:32:38,880
It's a friend of mine.

718
00:32:41,040 --> 00:32:42,200
Classic beginning.

719
00:32:43,120 --> 00:32:43,800
No.

720
00:32:44,520 --> 00:32:45,680
She's really a friend of mine.

721
00:32:45,840 --> 00:32:47,400
OK, a friend of yours.

722
00:32:47,680 --> 00:32:48,200
Then what?

723
00:32:51,080 --> 00:32:52,360
This friend of mine

724
00:32:52,960 --> 00:32:55,160
met someone earlier.

725
00:32:56,960 --> 00:32:57,520
A man?

726
00:33:00,760 --> 00:33:01,920
At first,

727
00:33:02,360 --> 00:33:04,480
she thought this guy was nasty.

728
00:33:04,640 --> 00:33:05,600
He had better magic arts than her,

729
00:33:05,760 --> 00:33:06,600
better perception than her,

730
00:33:06,840 --> 00:33:07,880
and constantly bullied her.

731
00:33:09,080 --> 00:33:11,640
But then she realized

732
00:33:12,360 --> 00:33:14,240
that whenever she was in danger,

733
00:33:14,680 --> 00:33:17,120
that guy always stepped forward.

734
00:33:18,600 --> 00:33:20,520
He seemed to be good to her.

735
00:33:21,520 --> 00:33:22,160
Then...

736
00:33:22,880 --> 00:33:24,960
Then they got together.

737
00:33:25,920 --> 00:33:26,720
But...

738
00:33:27,080 --> 00:33:29,240
But they broke up afterwards?

739
00:33:33,120 --> 00:33:34,680
Because I...

740
00:33:35,880 --> 00:33:37,960
No, the friend of mine.

741
00:33:38,600 --> 00:33:39,720
She realized one day

742
00:33:40,200 --> 00:33:42,400
that all that guy had done for her

743
00:33:43,440 --> 00:33:45,480
was because she looked like

744
00:33:45,480 --> 00:33:46,760
his ex-girlfriend.

745
00:33:48,880 --> 00:33:53,200
Then she started quarreling with him.

746
00:33:53,520 --> 00:33:54,640
But it didn't work out.

747
00:33:58,920 --> 00:34:00,440
Does it bore you?

748
00:34:00,720 --> 00:34:01,240
No.

749
00:34:01,720 --> 00:34:02,200
I'm not bored.

750
00:34:03,880 --> 00:34:04,320
So,

751
00:34:06,040 --> 00:34:06,960
do you still like him?

752
00:34:08,120 --> 00:34:08,670
I...

753
00:34:09,920 --> 00:34:11,440
I suppose so.

754
00:34:15,960 --> 00:34:17,710
How could you trick me?

755
00:34:18,840 --> 00:34:19,960
I didn't.

756
00:34:20,440 --> 00:34:21,000
Sit down.

757
00:34:21,750 --> 00:34:23,320
Let me give you some real advice.

758
00:34:24,560 --> 00:34:26,750
What did he tell you?

759
00:34:30,120 --> 00:34:33,520
He said he never thought of me
as a substitute.

760
00:34:34,440 --> 00:34:37,080
But I don't feel good about it.

761
00:34:37,640 --> 00:34:38,880
I feel jealous.

762
00:34:39,190 --> 00:34:41,880
You feel jealous
because you don't trust him.

763
00:34:42,640 --> 00:34:44,040
Because he isn't doing the right thing.

764
00:34:44,710 --> 00:34:46,160
You'd better forget about the man

765
00:34:46,160 --> 00:34:47,230
who treats you like a substitute.

766
00:34:47,960 --> 00:34:49,880
Such kind of man
doesn't deserve to live.

767
00:34:52,120 --> 00:34:52,440
OK.

768
00:34:52,670 --> 00:34:53,520
Don't be mad.

769
00:34:53,600 --> 00:34:54,480
Don't be mad.

770
00:34:57,000 --> 00:34:58,720
I recalled my best friend.

771
00:35:00,120 --> 00:35:01,640
She sacrificed her life

772
00:35:01,680 --> 00:35:02,800
because of a man.

773
00:35:03,720 --> 00:35:05,480
I won't allow you
to make the same mistake.

774
00:35:12,040 --> 00:35:13,480
By the way,

775
00:35:14,240 --> 00:35:15,960
I always carry this jade pendant
with me.

776
00:35:16,960 --> 00:35:18,240
It means a lot to me.

777
00:35:19,360 --> 00:35:20,360
I want you to have it.

778
00:35:21,040 --> 00:35:21,680
No.

779
00:35:22,120 --> 00:35:23,800
It's precious to you.

780
00:35:24,800 --> 00:35:25,440
I can't take it.

781
00:35:25,600 --> 00:35:27,080
Don't you consider me a good friend?

782
00:35:27,440 --> 00:35:28,320
I do.

783
00:35:28,400 --> 00:35:29,960
Then put it on.

784
00:35:35,600 --> 00:35:36,240
Thank you.

785
00:35:39,720 --> 00:35:40,200
Tantan,

786
00:35:42,880 --> 00:35:47,360
have you ever considered other men?

787
00:35:49,520 --> 00:35:50,440
Other men?

788
00:35:52,040 --> 00:35:52,680
Like

789
00:35:53,960 --> 00:35:54,600
Qiu Yuebai?

790
00:35:57,000 --> 00:35:58,320
I've been observing him
over the past few days.

791
00:35:59,040 --> 00:36:00,600
I think he has a good character
and career.

792
00:36:01,440 --> 00:36:02,840
And he risked his life

793
00:36:02,880 --> 00:36:04,120
to save you in the quicksand pit.

794
00:36:04,840 --> 00:36:05,880
Above all,

795
00:36:06,960 --> 00:36:08,960
I think he loves you with all his heart.

796
00:36:11,280 --> 00:36:12,040
But, I...

797
00:36:13,040 --> 00:36:14,480
But I don't love him.

798
00:36:15,760 --> 00:36:17,720
You can spend more time
bonding with him.

799
00:36:17,760 --> 00:36:19,160
You can try to accept him.

800
00:36:20,480 --> 00:36:20,840
I...

801
00:36:21,200 --> 00:36:22,560
Don't rush into any decisions.

802
00:36:23,280 --> 00:36:24,640
Think it over.

